title: JeweliX [CRACK]
description:
Welcome to the world of Jewelix - a place of stunning jewelry, picky customers and commercial success! Everything depends on your sharp eye, strategic thinking and communication skills as you try your hand at creating stunning brooches, sparkling earrings and more! Master the art of selling to many different types of customers, each with their own tastes and preferences. Polish your skills in this dazzling puzzler and make your jewelry store the most popular place in town!


Exciting Action game with the following features :

Create More Than 100 Different Jewelry Pieces!
Sell To Many Types Of Customers!
Over 90 Sparkling Levels!
Test Your Communication Skills!
System Requirements

OS: Windows 98, Windows 2000, Windows XP, Windows Vista Memory: 256 MB DirectX: 8.0 or later CPU: P 1.0GHz Video: 16MB Video Card

Installation:
1. Install
2. Copy "Jewelix.exe" to the installation folder
3. Play :)
